dmca.title: Our Client: J.L. Bates, LLC
dmca.body:
This law firm represents J.1. Bates, LLC ("JLB"). I am writing concerning the Office  Lease by and between JLB and Go Daddy Software, Inc. ("Go Daddy") dated November 18, 2004,  which has been posted on the oneCLE website. At this time, I do not know how long the Lease has  been posted on the website or how oneCLE obtained it. The Lease is proprietary information of JLB  and oneCLE has not obtained the permission, consent or authority of either JLB or Go Daddy to  publish the Lease.

The purpose of this letter is to demand that oneCLE immediately remove the Lease  from the website and any other website within the control or ownership of oneCLE. Pursuant to A.R.S.
